adjectives.description: fictive (comparative more fictive, superlative most fictive)

entries.meaning: Having the characteristics of fiction: fictional.
Resulting from imaginative creation: fanciful or invented.
(Internet slang) In claimed cases of dissociative identity disorder: an introject based on a character from a fictional work.
examples: I am constantly scared to text my friends while I front because a lot people were telling me that fictives especially from dsmp/genshin aren't valid. That makes me genuinely sad, I am afraid to receive any form of hate from my friends or even get fakeclaimed.
